{"id":263,"parent_id":262,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":263,"title":"3 John 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"3 Jn.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Third Epistle of",["br"],["span.dominant","John"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","John commends Gaius for his help to those who love the truth."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.1","order":"03.27.001.26887"},["b","1"],"The elder unto the wellbeloved Gaius, whom I love in the truth."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.2","order":"03.27.001.26888"},["b","2"],"Beloved, I wish above all things that thou mayest prosper and be in health, even as thy soul prospereth."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.3","order":"03.27.001.26889"},["b","3"],"For I rejoiced greatly, when the brethren came and testified of the truth that is in thee, even as thou walkest in the truth."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.4","order":"03.27.001.26890"},["b","4"],"I have no greater",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"joy"],"than to hear that my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"children"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"walk"],"in truth."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.5","order":"03.27.001.26891"},["b","5"],"Beloved, thou doest faithfully whatsoever thou doest to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"brethren"],", and to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"strangers"],";"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.6","order":"03.27.001.26892"},["b","6"],"Which have borne witness of thy charity before the church: whom if thou bring forward on their journey after a godly sort, thou shalt do well:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.7","order":"03.27.001.26893"},["b","7"],"Because that for his name’s sake they went forth, taking nothing of the Gentiles."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.8","order":"03.27.001.26894"},["b","8"],"We therefore ought to receive such, that we might be fellowhelpers to the truth."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.9","order":"03.27.001.26895"},["b","9"],"I wrote unto the church: but Diotrephes, who loveth to have the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"preeminence"],"among them,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"receiveth"],"us not."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.10","order":"03.27.001.26896"},["b","10"],"Wherefore, if I come, I will remember his deeds which he doeth,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"prating"],"against us with malicious words: and not content therewith, neither doth he himself receive the brethren, and forbiddeth them that would, and casteth",["i","them"],"out of the church."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.11","order":"03.27.001.26897"},["b","11"],"Beloved, follow not that which is evil, but that which is good. He that doeth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"good"],"is of God: but he that doeth evil hath not seen God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.12","order":"03.27.001.26898"},["b","12"],"Demetrius hath good report of all",["i","men,"],"and of the truth itself: yea, and we",["i","also"],"bear record; and ye know that our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"record"],"is true."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.13","order":"03.27.001.26899"},["b","13"],"I had many things to write, but I will not with ink and pen",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"write"],"unto thee:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.14","order":"03.27.001.26900"},["b","14"],"But I trust I shall shortly see thee, and we shall speak face to face. Peace",["i","be"],"to thee.",["i","Our"],"friends salute thee. Greet the friends by name."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.4a","order":"03.27.001.26901"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joy"},"TG Joy"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.4b","order":"03.27.001.26903"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/5.21"},"1 Jn. 5:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.4c","order":"03.27.001.26905"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.5a","order":"03.27.001.26907"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.88.88-92"},"D&C 84:88 (88–92)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.5b","order":"03.27.001.26909"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.9a","order":"03.27.001.26911"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unrighteous-dominion"},"TG Unrighteous Dominion"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.9b","order":"03.27.001.26913"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.10a","order":"03.27.001.26915"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/16.3"},"Num. 16:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.11a","order":"03.27.001.26917"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.12"},"Moro. 7:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.12a","order":"03.27.001.26919"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"witness, testimony."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.13a","order":"03.27.001.26921"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."]]}
